  "title": "Technical Buyer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Procurement:</strong></p><ul><li>Source services and materials for all Singapore functions in co-operation with procurement.</li><li>Run procurement process in co-operation with Singapore departments from supplier identification to purchase order and material receiving.</li><li>Participate in commercial negotiations with material and service providers.</li><li>Arrange expediting of critical orders.</li><li>Maintain list for preferred suppliers and negotiate frame contracts with selected suppliers.</li><li>Arrange archiving of contracts and other commercial documents.</li><li>Optimise vendor base and continue to look for competitive and reliable source.</li><li>Identify opportunity that can add value and generate cost optimisation.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's degree or equivalent experience in purchasing, inventory, or supply chain management.</li><li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills.</li><li>Hands on experience in using SAP.</li></ul>",
